{% extends "base.html.twig" %}

{% block title %}Safety Guidelines — Minoo{% endblock %}

{% block content %}
  <div class="content-section flow-lg">
    <div>
      <h1>Safety Guidelines</h1>
      <p class="text-secondary">Your safety and the safety of Elders is our priority.</p>
    </div>

    <section class="flow">
      <h2>For Elders</h2>
      <ul class="how-it-works__list">
        <li>You will always be contacted by phone before any visit</li>
        <li>You are never obligated to accept help — you can decline at any time</li>
        <li>Volunteers are matched through coordinators who know your community</li>
        <li>If anything feels wrong, contact your coordinator immediately</li>
        <li>Never share financial information or give money to a volunteer</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="flow">
      <h2>For Volunteers</h2>
      <ul class="how-it-works__list">
        <li>Always contact the Elder by phone before visiting</li>
        <li>Respect the Elder's home, privacy, and boundaries</li>
        <li>Only provide the type of help that was requested</li>
        <li>Never accept money or gifts for your service</li>
        <li>Report any concerns to your coordinator right away</li>
        <li>If you feel unsafe at any time, leave and contact the coordinator</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="flow">
      <h2>What to Expect</h2>
      <p>All support is coordinated through a community coordinator. The coordinator:</p>
      <ul class="how-it-works__list">
        <li>Reviews every request before assigning a volunteer</li>
        <li>Matches volunteers based on location, skills, and availability</li>
        <li>Follows up after every visit to check on both the Elder and volunteer</li>
        <li>Is available to address any concerns or issues</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="flow">
      <h2>Reporting Concerns</h2>
      <p>If you have any safety concerns about a volunteer visit, contact your community coordinator. You can also reach the Minoo team through your dashboard.</p>
      <div class="safety-callout">
        <p><strong>In an emergency, always call 911.</strong></p>
        <p>For non-emergency community support, contact your band office or local social services.</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <div class="hero__actions">
      <a href="/elders" class="btn btn--primary">Request Help</a>
      <a href="/volunteer" class="btn btn--secondary">Volunteer</a>
    </div>
  </div>
{% endblock %}
